video_title: The more she LIKES YOU, the greater the DISCOUNT
transcript:
when it comes to women all men pay one
way or another there's this fantastic
scene in the movie Jack Reacher where
Jack played by Tom Cruise is approached
by a very attractive young woman in a
bar she makes it very clear that she
would like to leave with him and he
replies that he can't afford her and she
indignantly responds that she's not a
hooker he replies that well then he
really can't afford her and this
exchange makes people laugh because like
all good jokes there's some truth to it
in general when it comes to women the
more transactional the relationship the
less you actually pay
